===Verb===
{{ja-verb|k|type=3|hira=さんすうする|rom=sansūsuru}}
# to do [[arithmetic]]; to [[calculate]]
#: ただ計算方法を教えるのではなく、算数する心を育むことが大切だ。
#: It is important to foster an arithmetic way of thinking, rather than merely to teach how to calculate.

====Synonym====
*[[計算する]](けいさんする, ''keisansuru'')

====Usage notes====
*This type3 verb form with 算数 is quite rare. Instead, use "[[計算する]]" ([[keisan suru|keisán surú]]) to mean "to calculate".

